name: The Wonderful World of Monsters & Lovers

metadata.name: The Hunting Librarian
metadata.description:
Librarian, one of underestimated, underrated profiles a person does for a living, keeps the key to knowledge. The librarian knowledge, combined with outer realm physical attributes, give the estranged one a latent dangerous trait for those who oppress.

Created with heart & soul. Presenting in 4K for you to reflect.
